{"id":"ea2806bb-f6bd-4f45-85fe-46fd7511b7c9", "recipient":"37c98387-ac01-45fb-ad5f-0d985d8c71c5", "sender":"0366df6f-24ee-4e31-87f9-43bad5e6ad4d", "priority":"MESSAGE_PRIORITY_HIGH", "timestamp":"2026-05-31T20:06:31.325663500Z", "renderDetails":{"messageTitle":"Message from Web Browser (browser)"}, "content":"I apologize, but I still cannot connect to Chrome. The `chrome_devtools` MCP server is hardcoded to look for the `DevToolsActivePort` file at `C:\\Users\\smile\\AppData\\Local\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\DevToolsActivePort`. \n\nEven though Chrome is running on port 9222, the tool cannot find this file. Could you please relaunch Chrome and ensure it uses the default user data directory so that the `DevToolsActivePort` file is created in that specific location? Once that is done, I will be able to access the YouTube URL and extract the requested information.", "sourceMetadata":{"tool":{"conversationId":"0366df6f-24ee-4e31-87f9-43bad5e6ad4d", "stepIndex":24, "toolCall":{"id":"8j9madlq", "name":"send_message", "argumentsJson":"{\"Message\":\"I apologize, but I still cannot connect to Chrome. The `chrome_devtools` MCP server is hardcoded to look for the `DevToolsActivePort` file at `C:\\\\Users\\\\smile\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Google\\\\Chrome\\\\User Data\\\\DevToolsActivePort`. \\n\\nEven though Chrome is running on port 9222, the tool cannot find this file. Could you please relaunch Chrome and ensure it uses the default user data directory so that the `DevToolsActivePort` file is created in that specific location? Once that is done, I will be able to access the YouTube URL and extract the requested information.\",\"Recipient\":\"37c98387-ac01-45fb-ad5f-0d985d8c71c5\",\"toolAction\":\"Requesting Chrome relaunch\",\"toolSummary\":\"Request Chrome relaunch\"}", "thinkingSignature":"", "originalName":"send_message"}}}}